{"tid":1733823,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【南海十三郎】遭港團員割席取消重演　高志森：香港演藝人不要自視過高！","createTime":"2019-11-18T07:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T11:56:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d07b933d333f1263002c739f5c6ea19bc39df35a","tid":1733823,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:45:11.000Z","msg":"網傳高志森被《南海十三郎》舞台劇的台前幕後工作人員割席，以致明年四月的演出取消！有香港傳媒聯絡高導演求證，但對方沒有回覆；然而網上則流傳一個名為「南海2016巡迴演員」的WhatsApp群組的一訊息。一位名為「KO CHI SUM」英文譯名的人士以短訊表示：明年西九就不演了，更表示「中國市場很大！香港演藝人也不要自視過高了&hellip;」，「我團絕對可以演一個沒有任何香港台前幕後參與的南海十三郎，巡演全國！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1573983741_d55d_5dd215c236f87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F1573983741_d55d_5dd215c236f87.jpg&h=aae605d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n訊息內容為：「大家別亂傳了、暴徒亂港，治安不好，明年西九就不演了。所謂的「杯葛者」也就不用圍爐取暖了。我團絕對可以演一個沒有任何香港台前幕後參與的南海十三郎，巡演全國！天大地大，中國市場很大！香港演藝人也就不要自視過高了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.modia.com.hk/2019/11/18/151920/%E3%80%90%E7%B5%84%E6%88%90%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%98%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%91%E9%81%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%98%E5%93%A1%E5%89%B2%E5%B8%AD%E3%80%80%E9%AB%98%E5%BF%97%E6%A3%AE%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%BC%94/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2019%2F11%2F18%2F151920%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25B5%2584%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2598%25EF%25BC%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%2598%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2589%25B2%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25BF%2597%25E6%25A3%25AE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BC%2594%2F&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2YlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=6b98945b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.modia.com.hk/2019/11/18/151920/%E3%80%90%E7%B5%84%E6%88%90%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%98%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%91%E9%81%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%98%E5%93%A1%E5%89%B2%E5%B8%AD%E3%80%80%E9%AB%98%E5%BF%97%E6%A3%AE%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%BC%94/</a>"},{"pid":"e3c9f3b14e2f5cc3aebdabf46366c7670b19be78","tid":1733823,"uid":153679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"零願畀錢睇套全港人講粗口既南海13郎<br />\n都唔睇奶共13郎"},{"pid":"49c2fa6550bd4210d54ece0478f17189e4498386","tid":1733823,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}